data.description: Wonderful treed lot with room to relax. Located in the Beacon Point community, private beach access, community pool, playground & gathering area. Community water system, power on lot, septic installed & potential to build a cabin or use for an RV site. Lot comes with a storage shed & driveway is in. Great getaway lot to come enjoy Hood Canal and all the recreational opportunities in the area. Community features include private beach access & boat launch, oyster limit per day.
